      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and followed every maintenance check to the letter. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
