    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained to exacting standards. This example features the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine with its sophisticated sequential twin-turbocharger system providing seamless boost across the rev range. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, benefiting from Mazda\u2019s lightweight Power Plant Frame (PPF) and a perfectly balanced 50/50 weight distribution. Mechanical highlights include the original 5-speed manual transmission with crisp synchronizer engagement and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The double-wishbone suspension components are pristine, ensuring precise kinematic response. Zero fluid leaks, original R134a AC system, and a documented maintenance history confirm its mechanical integrity. This is a turn-key performance icon for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
