      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom quality.' This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows in every square inch. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero imperfections, stone chips, or swirls. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and tight, still carrying that distinct new-car scent, with every button and digital display functioning exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; the engine purrs with silent precision, and the transmission shifts are imperceptible. This isn't just a used car; it\u2019s a collector-grade specimen for the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. Complete service records and both original keys included.",
